    "custom_liquid_LM3Gng": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "name": "Custom Liquid",
      "settings": {
        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": false,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<div class=\"tm-testimonials-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"tm-custom-container\">\n    <h2 class=\"tm-main-title\">What Some Of Our Satisfied Customers Are Saying</h2>\n    <div class=\"tm-custom-grid\">\n      \n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"My cycle has been more regular since I started.\nI was diagnosed with PCOS two years ago. My gynecologist recommended I work on inflammation and hormonal balance naturally. After 6 weeks of Phytoseed Labs, my cycle became noticeably more regular and my energy through the luteal phase improved.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Heather D.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I do a seasonal gut detox every year and Phytoseed Labs has replaced my old protocol entirely. The combination of oregano and black seed oil is just more complete — I feel lighter, cleaner, and my skin even cleared up.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Mary B.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"After years of unexplained fatigue and digestive discomfort, I started researching natural anti-parasitic options. Oregano oil and black seed oil kept coming up — Phytoseed Labs combines both at real potency. This is the one that actually worked.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Daniel M.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I'd returned from travel with persistent gut issues. My naturopath pointed to a potential parasite load. Phytoseed Labs was her exact recommendation. Four weeks later my stool test came back clean and I feel incredible.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Thomas V.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"The bloating, the gas, the constant discomfort after meals — gone. Phytoseed Labs worked quietly in the background and one day I just realized my gut had never felt this calm. Highly recommend for anyone doing a natural cleanse.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Sophia L.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I'd been dealing with bloating and heaviness for months. My gut just felt off. I really needed a natural detox. After two weeks with Phytoseed Labs I felt genuinely clean inside for the first time in years. It's like a natural reset.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Nicolas B.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I've had IBS for years and honestly didn't expect much — I've tried everything. Two weeks in, the stomach cramping and rumbling that was basically my daily life has calmed right down. My stomach just feels quieter. Can't explain it but I'll take it.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Chloe B.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I started this for immune support — kept getting every bug going around at work. But the unexpected thing was my skin. My naturopath always said skin issues start in the gut and I think she was right. Four weeks in and my digestion is calmer AND my complexion has cleared up. Bit of a bonus I didn't see coming.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Amelie M.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I've been dealing with suspected Candida overgrowth and was told to try oregano oil — it's well known in the natural health community for that. Found Phytoseed Labs and liked that it also had black seed oil in there. First week felt like a proper detox reaction, then everything started to settle. My digestion hasn't felt this normal in years.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Andrew T.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"I've used oil of oregano for years but always avoided liquid tinctures because they're harsh and inconvenient. These softgels completely solve that problem. The potency is clearly there.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Camilla H.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★☆</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">For two years I just accepted that feeling bloated, heavy, and exhausted was normal for me. I tried cutting foods out, going to the GP, spending a fortune on probiotics. Nothing really moved the needle. A friend mentioned Phytoseed Labs almost in passing and honestly I only ordered it because I'd run out of other ideas. By week three something had genuinely shifted. My stomach was calm, I wasn't waking up tired, and the brain fog I'd just learned to live with started to lift. I nearly cried the first morning I got up and actually felt like myself. Don't wait as long as I did.</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Alexander P.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">I'd seen Phytoseed Labs come up a few times. I was sceptical. Meanwhile I was dealing with chronic gut discomfort, low energy, and what I now think was a low-grade parasitic load I'd picked up and never fully cleared. Eight months of feeling off and doing nothing about it. When I finally ordered, I noticed a difference by day four. The heaviness in my gut started clearing, the constant post-meal fatigue eased off, and by week three my partner asked if I'd changed something because I seemed like myself again.</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Rachel Y.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tm-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"tm-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"tm-review-content\">\"15 years of bloating. 15 years of being told 'irritable bowel.' In 3 weeks of treatment, my stomach deflated by 60%. My gastroenterologist asked me what I had done.\"</p>\n        <div class=\"tm-review-meta\">Denis T.</div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n  .tm-testimonials-wrapper {\n    display: block !important;\n    width: 100% !important;\n    padding: 60px 0 !important;\n    background-color: #f8fafc !important;\n    clear: both !important;\n  }\n  .tm-custom-container {\n    max-width: 1200px !important;\n    margin: 0 auto !important;\n    padding: 0 20px !important;\n  }\n  .tm-main-title {\n    text-align: center !important;\n    margin-bottom: 40px !important;\n    font-size: 28px !important;\n    color: #1a1a1a !important;\n    font-weight: bold !important;\n    font-family: sans-serif !important;\n  }\n  /* CHANGEMENT ICI : Flexbox pour l'alignement horizontal */\n  .tm-custom-grid {\n    display: flex !important;\n    overflow-x: auto !important;\n    gap: 25px !important;\n    padding-bottom: 20px !important; /* Espace pour la barre de défilement */\n    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory !important; /* Effet de blocage sur chaque carte */\n    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch !important;\n  }\n  /* Cacher la barre de défilement pour un look plus propre (optionnel) */\n  .tm-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar {\n    height: 6px;\n  }\n  .tm-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {\n    background: #cbd5e1;\n    border-radius: 10px;\n  }\n\n  .tm-review-card {\n    background: #ffffff !important;\n    padding: 25px !important;\n    border-radius: 12px !important;\n    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1) !important;\n    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0 !important;\n    display: flex !important;\n    flex-direction: column !important;\n    /* CHANGEMENT ICI : Largeur fixe pour les cartes */\n    min-width: 320px !important;\n    max-width: 320px !important;\n    scroll-snap-align: start !important;\n  }\n  .tm-stars-display {\n    color: #fbbf24 !important;\n    margin-bottom: 12px !important;\n    font-size: 1.2rem !important;\n    display: block !important;\n  }\n  .tm-review-content {\n    font-size: 14px !important;\n    color: #475569 !important;\n    line-height: 1.6 !important;\n    font-style: italic !important;\n    margin: 0 0 20px 0 !important;\n    flex-grow: 1 !important;\n    display: block !important;\n    font-family: sans-serif !important;\n  }\n  .tm-review-meta {\n    font-weight: bold !important;\n    font-size: 13px !important;\n    color: #1a1a1a !important;\n    border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9 !important;\n    padding-top: 12px !important;\n    margin-top: auto !important;\n    display: block !important;\n    font-family: sans-serif !important;\n  }\n\n  /* Sur mobile, on garde le même comportement horizontal */\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .tm-review-card {\n      min-width: 280px !important;\n    }\n  }\n</style>",
        "background": "#aad7b0",
        "background_gradient": "",
        "text_color": ""
      }
    },
