        "liquid": "<div class=\"ps-testimonials-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"ps-custom-container\">\n\n    <div class=\"ps-heading-block\">\n      <span class=\"ps-badge\">★★★★★ TRUSTED BY +7000 people</span>\n      <h2 class=\"ps-main-title\">\n        What our community is Saying About <span>Phytoseed Labs</span>\n      </h2>\n      <p class=\"ps-subtitle\">\n        Natural gut support, immune balance & daily wellness — without harsh ingredients.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"ps-custom-grid\">\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          “My cycle has been more regular since I started. My energy through the luteal phase improved dramatically.”\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Heather D.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"My cycle has been more regular since I started.\nI was diagnosed with PCOS two years ago. My gynecologist recommended I work on inflammation and hormonal balance naturally. After 6 weeks of Phytoseed Labs, my cycle became noticeably more regular and my energy through the luteal phase improved.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Mary B.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"I do a seasonal gut detox every year and Phytoseed Labs has replaced my old protocol entirely. The combination of oregano and black seed oil is just more complete — I feel lighter, cleaner, and my skin even cleared up.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Daniel M.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"After years of unexplained fatigue and digestive discomfort, I started researching natural anti-parasitic options. Oregano oil and black seed oil kept coming up — Phytoseed Labs combines both at real potency. This is the one that actually worked.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Sophia L.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          \"I've had IBS for years and honestly didn't expect much — I've tried everything. Two weeks in, the stomach cramping and rumbling that was basically my daily life has calmed right down. My stomach just feels quieter. Can't explain it but I'll take it.\"\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Camilla H.</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"ps-review-card\">\n        <div class=\"ps-stars-display\">★★★★★</div>\n        <p class=\"ps-review-content\">\n          “I started taking Phytoseed Labs after reading about black seed oil and male fertility. After about 2 months, my energy improved, digestion felt better, and my latest fertility check showed improvements in motility and overall sperm quality. I also appreciate that it doesn’t have the harsh taste of liquid oregano oil. Definitely feels like a premium formula.”\n        </p>\n        <div class=\"ps-review-meta\">Arthur R.</div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<style>\n.ps-testimonials-wrapper{\n  width:100%;\n  padding:80px 0;\n  background:\n  linear-gradient(\n    180deg,\n    #eef4e8 0%,\n    #f8f5ef 100%\n  );\n  overflow:hidden;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-container{\n  max-width:1250px;\n  margin:0 auto;\n  padding:0 20px;\n}\n\n.ps-heading-block{\n  text-align:center;\n  margin-bottom:50px;\n}\n\n.ps-badge{\n  display:inline-block;\n  background:#4F5F35;\n  color:#F8F5EF;\n  padding:10px 18px;\n  border-radius:999px;\n  font-size:12px;\n  letter-spacing:2px;\n  font-weight:700;\n  margin-bottom:22px;\n}\n\n.ps-main-title{\n  font-size:52px;\n  line-height:1.1;\n  color:#2E3B22;\n  margin:0;\n  font-weight:700;\n  letter-spacing:-1px;\n}\n\n.ps-main-title span{\n  color:#4F5F35;\n}\n\n.ps-subtitle{\n  max-width:760px;\n  margin:18px auto 0;\n  font-size:18px;\n  line-height:1.7;\n  color:#72825B;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid{\n  display:flex;\n  overflow-x:auto;\n  gap:28px;\n  padding-bottom:20px;\n  scroll-snap-type:x mandatory;\n  -webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar{\n  height:6px;\n}\n\n.ps-custom-grid::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{\n  background:#cbb98d;\n  border-radius:20px;\n}\n\n.ps-review-card{\n  min-width:360px;\n  max-width:360px;\n  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.78);\n  backdrop-filter:blur(10px);\n  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.6);\n  border-radius:28px;\n  padding:32px;\n  box-shadow:\n  0 10px 35px rgba(79,95,53,0.08);\n  scroll-snap-align:start;\n  transition:all .3s ease;\n}\n\n.ps-review-card:hover{\n  transform:translateY(-5px);\n  box-shadow:\n  0 18px 45px rgba(79,95,53,0.12);\n}\n\n.ps-stars-display{\n  color:#B79A5B;\n  font-size:22px;\n  letter-spacing:4px;\n  margin-bottom:18px;\n}\n\n.ps-review-content{\n  color:#3f4b34;\n  font-size:16px;\n  line-height:1.8;\n  margin-bottom:24px;\n  font-style:italic;\n}\n\n.ps-review-meta{\n  border-top:1px solid #e7ddcb;\n  padding-top:16px;\n  font-size:13px;\n  font-weight:700;\n  letter-spacing:1px;\n  text-transform:uppercase;\n  color:#4F5F35;\n}\n\n@media(max-width:768px){\n\n  .ps-testimonials-wrapper{\n    padding:60px 0;\n  }\n\n  .ps-main-title{\n    font-size:34px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-subtitle{\n    font-size:16px;\n  }\n\n  .ps-review-card{\n    min-width:300px;\n    max-width:300px;\n    padding:26px;\n  }\n\n}\n</style>",
